                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable L</hi> 31.) I took the prisoner—he said, "I have not had the money, why is not <hi rend="italic">Jim</hi> here?"—he said, "<hi rend="italic">Jim</hi> was with us at the time, he ought to be here as well as me."</p>
