                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined. Q.</hi> Did <hi rend="italic">Jim</hi> wrestle with you? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No, he did not touch me—I am quite sure of that—I knew the prisoner by sight before—they did not go away in the same direction—<hi rend="italic">Jim</hi> went with me—I knew him by sight, and the prisoner too—I do not know how he gets his living.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> We were both wrestling, and fell down; a man came by and picked him up.</p>
